data.title: Neurosurgery, Spine Surgery
data.meta_description: Dr. Justin Davis is certified by the American Board of Neurological Surgery. He earned his medical degree from the University of Kansas School of Medicine and completed his residency at the University of Kentucky Albert B. Chandler Hospital.  Practice Locations: Overland Park, KS, Kansas City, KS. Specialties: Neurosurgery, Spine Surgery.
